Purpose: Protects AWS workloads from DDoS attacks.

Types:
Shield Standard: Free, automatically included for all AWS customers. Protects against common Layer 3/4 DDoS attacks.
Shield Advanced: Paid tier with enhanced protection, real-time attack visibility, cost protection against scaling charges, and access to the AWS DDoS Response Team (DRT).

Use Case Example: 
During a product launch, if your site is hit with a massive DDoS attack, Shield absorbs the traffic to keep your application online.
